description: Enterprise Management Company was formerly known as Yang’s Inc headquartered in Watertown. The company name was changed in 2010 to better reflect our business directions and expansions.Our company is very active in Boston’s Chinese community. Our board members are regularly involved in different fund raising and charity events. We are determined to be part of the effort to make our city a better place to live.Over the past 18 years of serving the greater Boston area, we have operated and managed several Chinese restaurants and food trucks. Our food and services are well known and well received by our customers. We cater to your needs by providing high quality and economical meals that will appease everybody’s taste and budget.
name: Savory Food Truck
